@page "/dam/help"
@inject NavigationManager Navigation

<style>
    .help-container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        font-family: sans-serif;
    }

    .help-container h3 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .help-container ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .help-container li {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .help-container li p {
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
    }
</style>


<div class="help-container">
    <h3>Help Page</h3>
    <p>Welcome to the help page. Here you can look up information on how to operate the DAM system.</p>

    <h4>Pages Overview</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>
            📦 <strong><NavLink href="/dam/products">Products</NavLink></strong>
            <p>The 📦 Products page contains all the products.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            🖼️ <strong><NavLink href="/dam/assets">Assets</NavLink></strong>
            <p>The 🖼️ Assets page contains all the assets. On the page you can upload new assets,
                search for assets, and filter the assets with their specific tags.
                If you click on an asset it's possible to edit the assets.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            🏷️ <strong><NavLink href="/dam/tags">Tags</NavLink></strong>
            <p>The 🏷️ Tags page contains all the tags. On the page you can add and delete tags.</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>